================================================================================
Provenance
================================================================================

Upstream:  HACL* / Project Everest — https://github.com/hacl-star/hacl-star
           (obtained via the `hacl-star` OCaml package, version 0.4.5).
Subset:    only the portable-C primitives needed for TLS_CHACHA20_POLY1305_SHA256
           with X25519 and Ed25519 (SHA-256/384, X25519, ChaCha20-Poly1305,
           HKDF/HMAC-SHA256, Ed25519) plus the kremlin headers they include.
           No vale assembly and no EverCrypt dispatch layer are included.
Changes:   none. The files are redistributed verbatim; their license headers are
           retained unmodified. kroopt's only added C is Kroopt/Native/kroopt_ffi.c
           (kroopt's own Apache-2.0 FFI glue), which is not part of HACL*.
